      "text": "Indemnification carve-outs are not explicitly defined in the clause.  This requires further clarification on which liabilities will be indemnified and by whom.",
      "severity": "major",
      "references": ["Indemnification"]
    }
  ],
  "favoursWhom": "non-operator" 
}

